- [ ] Test 2 verifies that wheel + scroll does report `isAtBottom: false`
- [ ] Test 3 verifies that the 150ms debounce clears the intent flag, using `vi.useFakeTimers()`
- [ ] `vi.useRealTimers()` called at end of Test 3 to prevent timer leaks
- [ ] All existing tests continue to pass
- [ ] `pnpm test -- --run` exits with zero failures

